OL,3,CCCTV captures moment man carries out
OL,4,Cmachete attack as children flee
OL,6,FA man has been jailed after wielding a
OL,7,Fmachete attack in a shop as children
OL,8,Fwere forced to flee in terror.
OL,10,FDale Dean began violently attacking
OL,11,Fhis victim with the huge blade at the
OL,12,Foff licence on Kentmere Road in
OL,13,FBreightmet, Bolton last year.
OL,15,FPolice raced to the scene at around
OL,16,F7.50pm on 5 April after reports of a
OL,17,Fman carrying a machete.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
