OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1771941809
OL,3,CCCTV captures moment man carries out
OL,4,Cmachete attack as children flee
OL,6,FWhen officers arrived, they found one
OL,7,Fman had been attacked, with the inside
OL,8,Fof the shop also badly left badly
OL,9,Fdamaged by Dean.
OL,11,FThe victim sustained several injuries
OL,12,Fincluding to his head and shoulder. He
OL,13,Fwas rushed to hospital following the
OL,14,Fincident and was struggling with
OL,15,Fsleeping and pain, a court heard.
OL,17,FFollowing the incident, police said
OL,18,Fthat the attack had also been
OL,19,Fwitnessed by other shoppers including
OL,20,Fchildren who 'must have been extremely
OL,21,Ffrightened'.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
