OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1771941809
OL,3,CCCTV captures moment man carries out
OL,4,Cmachete attack as children flee
OL,6,FFootage, exclusively shared with the
OL,7,FManchester Evening News, has shown the
OL,8,Fmoment Dean was seen standing beside
OL,9,Fthe till on his phone while holding a
OL,10,Fpacket of wipes. At the time, a mum
OL,11,Fand her two children are being served
OL,12,Fby the member of staff.
OL,14,FWithin a matter of seconds, two other
OL,15,Fmen enter the shop, at which point
OL,16,FDale is seen cutting through a
OL,17,Fdifferent aisle and suddenly charging
OL,18,Fat them with the huge blade. They run
OL,19,Fup the aisle and attempt to block Dale
OL,20,Fby throwing a shelf in his path.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1771941809
OL,3,CCCTV captures moment man carries out
OL,4,Cmachete attack as children flee
OL,6,FThe two children and their mum are
OL,7,Fseen cowering in the corner in terror
OL,8,Fas Dale again launches at one man and
OL,9,Fis seen slamming down the machete.
OL,11,FHe then proceeds to lean over the
OL,12,Fcounter repeatedly reign blows with
OL,13,Fthe knife, pushing off shelves of
OL,14,Fitems onto the floor. He climbs on top
OL,15,Fof the counter and again lashes down
OL,16,Fwith the blade before making off.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1771941809
OL,3,CCCTV captures moment man carries out
OL,4,Cmachete attack as children flee
OL,6,FGreater Manchester Police said Dean
OL,7,Falso caused 'extensive damage' to the
OL,8,Finside of the shop before fleeing the
OL,9,Fscene. He was later arrested after
OL,10,Fdetectives launched an investigation.
OL,12,FThe 27-year-old, of Upper West Grove
OL,13,Fin Manchester, plead guilty to causing
OL,14,Fgrievous bodily harm with intent,
OL,15,Fpossession of a bladed article and
OL,16,Faffray. He was jailed for six years at
OL,17,FManchester Crown Court on 20 February.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1771941809
OL,3,CCCTV captures moment man carries out
OL,4,Cmachete attack as children flee
OL,6,FThe court also imposed an additional
OL,7,F20month extended licence period upon
OL,8,Fhis release due to the seriousness of
OL,9,Fthe offence and the danger he poses to
OL,10,Fthe public.
OL,12,FDetective Constable Jordan Brown, of
OL,13,Fthe Bolton Criminal Investigation
OL,14,FDepartment, said: "This was a shocking
OL,15,Fand violent incident that left the
OL,16,Fvictim with serious injuries and
OL,17,Fcaused fear within the community.
OL,18,FDean's actions were deliberate,
OL,19,Fdangerous, and showed a blatant
OL,20,Fdisregard for the safety of others.
OL,26,@vD@SOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1771941809
OL,3,CCCTV captures moment man carries out
OL,4,Cmachete attack as children flee
OL,6,F"Dean used or threatened unlawful
OL,7,Fviolence, causing significant fear to
OL,8,Fthose nearby, and was found to be
OL,9,Fcarrying a machete without lawful
OL,10,Freason.
OL,12,F"We welcome today's sentence, which
OL,13,Freflects the gravity of the offences.
OL,14,FOur officers will continue to take
OL,15,Fdecisive action against those who
OL,16,Fcarry weapons and commit violent
OL,17,Foffences on our streets."
OL,26,@nD@AOUyD@YO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/7
